# EmailJS configuration
# Sign up at https://www.emailjs.com and create an email service + template.
#
# 1. VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID  — Email Services tab → your service ID (e.g. service_xxxxxxx)
# 2. VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID — Email Templates tab → your template ID (e.g. template_xxxxxxx)
# 3. VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY  — Account → General → Public Key (e.g. xxxxxxxxxxxxxx)
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your real values.
# The form sends enquiries to popupmax@gmail.com via the template you configure.

VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=your_template_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key_here
